  "name": "Devout Visionary",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/equipment/shield/pavise-wooden-wings-blue-white.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl26_LabelType\">As a child, you had a strange vision while suffering from a terrible illness, and only found your way back to the mundane world by following the call of a spiritual leader&mdash;perhaps a shaman&rsquo;s drum or a druid&rsquo;s lilting poetry. Since then, you have studied symbolism and dreams in the hope that you might understand your own vision, though your lessons prove just as helpful to others.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl26_LabelType\">You gain a +1 trait bonus on Will saving throws against spells and effects that grant the confused or dazed condition. Once per day as a full-round action, you may grant an adjacent ally a new Will saving throw to end an effect that grants the confused or dazed condition.</span></p>",
